{"tid":1804429,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何君堯 : 父母墳墓被毀  亦不會改變作風","createTime":"2019-12-31T03:54:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T05:03:32.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"351dd15bf9f81db3c17a9388b1a9c992fff9a71a","tid":1804429,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T03:54:30.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】今屆區議會任期最後一天，未能連任的何君堯將卸任。他接受本台專訪時指，有反思721當晚到元朗是政治觸覺不足，而在選舉期間遇襲、辦事處及父母墳墓遭破壞，不會影響他日後的作風。<br />\n<br />\n區選拉票時遇襲，何君堯之後亦失落議席，除了歸咎政治大環境，何君堯亦認為自己未有分配好時間，兼顧區議會及立法會的工作，至於721這一晚的事他都有反省。<br />\n<br />\n721事件後，辦事處遭受破壞，父母墳墓亦被毀，何君堯指這些針對性的攻擊不會改變他的作風。<br />\n<br />\n他指不會因區議會敗選而退縮，對於合乎原則的事，<span style=\"color: red;\">即使不獲主流民意支持，他仍會致力推動，例如基本法第二十三條立法。</span><br />\n<br />\n總結區議會選舉的票數，建制派在新界西的得票比例減少，2016年換屆選舉以末席晉身立法會的何君堯指感到有危機，未來會鞏固好鄉事、同鄉以及法律專業的票源。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=375040\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D375040&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJsQVtcXcndjic5JqfcA1BWo%3D&h=e4f72b10\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D375040&h=56fcd635\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=375040</a>"},{"pid":"0ca142dcea06150babcb26f280738f02c2ec86e0","tid":1804429,"uid":210669,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T03:56:55.000Z","msg":"佢應該係想自己訓埋落墳墓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e43bebd3168dca71e0bb6a877ca2fde39b3de612","tid":1804429,"uid":42548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T03:57:14.000Z","msg":"呿，理撚得你死，關我地咩x事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"163d9989c7fd4937250ae4cf48d3a0d12f6af731","tid":1804429,"uid":42548,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0ca142dcea06150babcb26f280738f02c2ec86e0"